  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Your Turn] When this Digimon would digivolve into a card
    with [Shaman] or [Wizard] in its traits, you may trash up to 3 of your security
    cards. For each security card trashed with this effect, reduce the digivolution
    cost by 1.'
